Requirement Analysis – StudentHub Portal

1. Introduction
StudentHub is a web-based student management portal designed to simplify academic and administrative tasks. It provides a centralized platform where students can access attendance, results, certificates, fees, events, feedback, and profile information.

Functional Requirements:
User Authentication
Student login using Student ID and password.
Secure logout.
Session management.

Dashboard
Display welcome message.
Quick navigation cards.
Notifications.
Upcoming events.

Student Profile
View student information.
Display department, semester, contact details.
Profile picture.

Attendance Module
View subject-wise attendance.
Display attendance percentage.
Show attendance status.

Results Module
Display semester-wise results.
SGPA and CGPA.
Subject-wise marks.

Certificates Module
View available certificates.
Download certificates.
Certificate status.

Fees Module
Display fee details.
Payment status.
Due amount.

Events Module
Display upcoming events.
Event description.
Registration button.

Feedback Module
Submit feedback.
Rating system.
Suggestions.

Contact Page
College contact information.
Email.
Phone number.
Address.

Non-Functional Requirements:
